        {{> compounds/real-result username="@jasmineregmi" badge="Hair" badge_color="badge-secondary" category="#hair" content="The entire collection together gave my skin the rejuvenation it needed. I have even more confidence in the way I feel because for me it’s always about the feeling more than the look."}}
        {{> compounds/real-result username="@talmeshak" badge="Tan" badge_color="badge-purple" category="#tan" content="My hair is soo tangle prone because it’s so fine and long and bleached, but I was able to run my fingers through it easily with the mask."}}
        {{> compounds/real-result username="@okevaaa" badge="Tan" badge_color="badge-purple" category="#tan" content="I have never used fake tan before and was nervous that I would be all orange and streaky but this looked so natural and I didn't get any streaks thanks to the awesome mitt and brush!! The smell is INCRED!"}}
